data.description: Welcome to your dream home situated on large lot in waterview community. The two-story foyer leads into open concept design, offering gleaming hardwood floors, two-story family room with abundant natural light, and gourmet kitchen that will delight any chef. Imagine hosting gatherings in the formal dining area or enjoying cozy evenings by the fireplace. The first floor also boasts a convenient bedroom with an adjacent full bath, ideal for guests or a home office. Take either of the two staircases upstairs to discover large bonus room, spacious secondary bedrooms, well-appointed bathroom, and laundry room. Retreat to the impressive primary suite, featuring large walk-in closet, soaking tub, and oversized shower. Enjoy entertaining in the large fenced backyard with covered patio and dedicated grill area. With security, smart home features, surround sound, new insulated garage door, extended driveway, and community dock this home has it all! 5k in Closing Costs! Open house 2/4, 12-2 pm.
